text: Yousuf Shaaban Shemis (; 16 July 1931 – 28 February 2021) was an Egyptian actor. He was born in Shubra, Egypt. His career lasted from 1958 until 2017. He was known There is a Man in our House, Mother of the Bride and My Wife, the Director General.
